title: "Exactly Certified Dispersive Functionals from Automated Search"
abstract: >-
  Code and data reproduction package for exact-arithmetic certified dispersive
  positivity bounds on the D=10 maximal-supergravity R^4 coefficient g_0,
  designed by an LLM-guided evolutionary search under an exact certifier.
